org.apache.calcite.prepare

类 Prepare

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.prepare.Prepare

  • public abstract class Prepare
extends Object
    Abstract base for classes that implement the process of preparing and executing SQL expressions.

      Interface by which validator and planner can read table metadata.

      • THREAD_EXPAND

        public static final TryThreadLocal<Boolean> THREAD_EXPAND
        Temporary, until [CALCITE-1045] Decorrelate sub-queries in Project and Join is fixed.

        The default is false, meaning do not expand queries during sql-to-rel, but a few tests override and set it to true. After CALCITE-1045 is fixed, remove those overrides and use false everywhere.
